trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
The VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection class allows you to programmatically access a collection of <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping> objects.
The collection can be accessed with either the key or the index.
